of frustration by horse camel and raft a man finally will be able 
to answer the eternal question daddy when will we be there 
a time of scary scientific discovery especially in genetic 
engineering when society will have to deal with the questions of 
whether man is ready to play god and is god ready to let him 
who will prevail among the soothsayers the prophets of a bright 
new world or the seers of doom and gloom in that trade history 
indicates that the optimists and the pessimists run about 
neckandneck 
so far the meek have not inherited the earth but neither has 
big brother the year 1984 came and went without 1984 the grim 
scenario of an ultratotalitarian state by george orwell freedom 
stirs in china mikhail gorbachev sits in stalins office in moscow 
the world has not exploded in a nuclear armageddon and the 
