editors note he was deformed at birth and when he was 2 his 
legs were amputated up to the pelvis but kenny easterday 15 
thumbs his nose at his handicap and ignores the stares of strangers 
preferring to walk on his hands rather than ride in a wheelchair 
his spunk inspired a frenchcanadian filmmaker to make a movie about 
his life called kid brother 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
fifteenyearold kenny easterday knows the 
sight of a 2foottall boy with half a body walking on his hands or 
zooming down the street on a skateboard causes heads to turn 
kennys been stared at for so long friends say he gets perturbed 
if people fail to notice him 
its part of his cockiness part of what has helped him to 
survive 
kenny calls it his style a tough spunky veneer to protect 
the kid inside him who has been poked prodded inspected and 
rejected all his life he insists by example more than words 
that hes no different from any other teenage boy 
i like tornup shirts jean jackets with holes in them long 
hair earrings and hardrock music and getting in trouble he 
says his straight brown hair hanging limply over the collar of his 
