<TEXT>
 
peewee herman had a farm eieio 
and on this farm he had a talking pig named vance a pony who 
could make pancakes and an entire circusful of strange but 
goodhearted performers 
here is peewee practicing animal husbandry and agricultural 
science with smashing success but failing miserably at making 
friends with the local townsfolk a bunch of certified sourpusses 
who clearly would like to string up our hero by his red bowtie 
the one exception is winnie the local school marm who seems 
truly smitten with the androgynous peewee something is wrong 
though her blond tresses snarl painfully under peewees caress 
and she persists in making him detestable eggsalad sandwiches for 
their lunch dates 
the problem becomes clear when the circus led by kris 
kristofferson drops in his yard a la oz after a storm here is the 
girl of his dreams gina the trapeze artist played by the comely 
italian actress valeria golino peewees in love 
peewee who is already a manturnedboy doesnt exactly turn 
back into a man in this picture but he does seem to be growing up 
whereas peewees big adventure saw him curling a painted lip at 
the prospect of a date with the local bikeshop bimbo big top 
finds him as a fullblown romantic leading man with lots of girl 
trouble a real makeout scene and even gasp sex represented 
in a discreet yet cornball way 
the story of how he wins over the poopy townspeople and helps the 
circus put on the best show ever is classic peewee as written 
produced and performed by his alter ego paul reubens full of all 
the fun stuff that makes his saturday morning show so enchanting 
the message here is that its ok to be different big top will 
make kids of all ages feel good about themselves 
by lisa levitt ryckman ap national writer 
</TEXT>
