love is about a troubled girl who doesnt respond to the love of 
her friends on the other end of the telescope mann duets 
with another noted wordsmith elvis costello 
if you think mann has a tough life consider shear whose band 
released its debut album a few months ago not only is all his dirty 
laundry being aired in public but his exgirlfriends record far 
outshines his 
by david bauder associated press writer 
