<TEXT>
pillsbury co gave up its 2month fight and 
agreed to a 568 billion takeover by british conglomerate grand 
metropolitan plc two days after major courtroom setbacks 
grand met will purchase all outstanding shares of pillsbury 
common stock for 66 per share in cash 3 higher than grand mets 
most recent tender offer which was made last week 
