eliminated 
this breakthrough agreement is unique among major railroads 
because we can now immediately run freight trains in the covered 
areas with a locomotive engineer a conductor and one breakman 
without phasing in the reduced crews through attrition of the 
workforce said john snow csx president and chief operating 
officer 
