receive a separation allowance of 50000 transfer to another 
location and receive up to 20000 in relocation expenses or accept 
a furlough with rights to return plus a 15000 payment 
snow said the contract efforts are part of csxts goal of 
reducing employment on its 19state rail system to 30000 employees 
while reducing its route milage to 15000 from 20000 miles 
