conditions without bargaining over them first with union leaders 
but parker ruled that the shuttle deal did not trigger the labor 
laws protections he noted that in september the courts had 
approved a far more severe scheduling constriction by eastern that 
involved 4000 layoffs the elimination of service to 14 cities and 
the curtailment of 15 percent of the carriers flights 
the impact of the sale to trump shuttle pales in comparison to 
the impact of the september 1988 schedule change the judge wrote 
the shuttle which employs 850 people and makes 62 flights daily 
has been one of easterns few profitmakers earning an annual 
average profit of 17 million over the last five years according to 
eastern spokesman robin matell overall eastern lost 2337 million 
over the first nine months of 1988 he said 
parker wrote that if the unions are right and the airline is not 
truly trying to improve itself then easterns executives are 
acting out a cruel hoax upon the government and the public 
the passage of time should prove whether this is true he 
said 
trump who testified before parker on dec 7 has vowed to boost 
morale at the shuttle and to recognize the unions but has declined 
to guarantee current wages for the employees eastern has offered to 
retain any shuttle workers who wish to remain with the company 
texas air announced in february that it would sell the shuttle 
for 225 million to a new subsidiary it planned to form but 
easterns unions blocked that transaction in the courts and texas 
air chairman frank lorenzo announced in july that the deal had been 
canceled 
since he acquired eastern the nations sixth largest carrier in 
1986 lorenzo has been embroiled in bitter disputes with the unions 
representing the carriers mechanics pilots and flight attendants 
lorenzo has sought wage concessions while the unions have countered 
with lobbying before congress and public relations campaigns 
the sale would give trump all 17 aircraft landing and takeoff 
slots at airports in boston new york and washington 14 airport 
gates and ground equipment 
