<TEXT>
black amp decker inc said monday it is 
voluntarily recalling two of its coffeemaking machines because of a 
possible fire hazard 
the units being recalled are white spacemaker plus tm thermal 
carafe coffeemakers model pdc401 and model pdc403 purchased after 
july 1988 
the company said that under certain circumstances the units may 
overheat creating a fire hazard 
owners were asked to stop using them and return them to the 
nearest black amp decker service center for a refund 
